                    <span>I enjoyed the book, even though I'm not in marketing. Found some interesting points.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Rules for Revolutionaries</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
                      <span>0</span>
